@startuml
title Final Project - Review Class Diagram

left to right direction
hide circle

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

skinparam Class {
  BorderColor #334155
  BackgroundColor white
  FontColor #0F172A
}

skinparam ArrowColor #475569

skinparam Note {
  BackgroundColor #F8FAFC
  BorderColor #CBD5E1
  FontColor #334155
}

class Review {
  +id: bigint
  +student_id: bigint
  +student_name: string
  +student_group: string
  +review_text: text
  +profile_picture_url: string
  +rating_score: decimal
  +likes_count: integer
  +dislikes_count: integer
  +uploaded_at: datetime

  --
  +student()
}

class User {
  +id: bigint
  +name: string
  +email: string
  +requested_role: string
}

Review "*" --> "1" User : student

note right of Review
Stores student feedback shown
on the public visitor page.

Visitors can like or dislike reviews,
which updates the rating score.
end note

note bottom of User
Only approved student users can
submit reviews after enrollment
in at least one class/group.
end note

@enduml